Feature: Get products

Background:
Given Sending request to get products end point

Scenario: Get all products
When A get request is sent to getAllProducts
Then Return list of products

Scenario: Get all products returns empty list 
When A get request is sent to getAllProducts
Then Throw exception that no products available

Scenario: Get products by id
When A get request is sent to getAllProducts with id {2}
Then Return product

Scenario: Get products by id returns null
When A get request is sent to getAllProducts with id {22}
Then Throw exception that product does not exist